DECLARE @DocKey INTEGER SET @DocKey = {?ServiceCallSubDocKey@}
-- Service call line: SELECT T0.callID, T0.createDate, T0.subject, T0.itemCode, T0.manufSN, T0.custmrName, T1.Name AS 'CallStatus' FROM OSCL T0 JOIN OSCS T1 ON T0.status = T1.statusId WHERE T0.insID = @DocKey

DECLARE @CardId INTEGER SET @CardId = {?DOCKEY@}
SELECT T0.custmrName, T3.Name AS 'ContactPerson', T0.manufSN, T0.internalSN, T0.itemCode, T0.itemName, T0.status, T0.deliveryNo, T0.dlvryDate, T1.Phone1, T2.lastName AS 'TechnicianLastName', T2.firstName AS 'TechnicianFirstName' FROM OINS T0 LEFT JOIN OCRD T1 ON T0.customer = T1.CardCode LEFT JOIN OHEM T2 ON T0.technician = T2.empID LEFT JOIN OCPR T3 ON T0.contactCod = T3.CntctCode WHERE T0.insID = @CardId
